#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.72"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.72:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.72:0.2"
msgid "8. Apaṇṇakavagga"
msgstr "8. Guaranteed"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: diṭṭhi-apaṇṇakapaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.72:0.3"
msgid "72. Sammādiṭṭhisutta"
msgstr "72. Right View"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.77"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.72:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu apaṇṇakappaṭipadaṃ "
"paṭipanno hoti, yoni cassa āraddhā hoti āsavānaṃ khayāya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when a mendicant has four things their practice is guaranteed, "
"and they have laid the groundwork for ending the defilements."

msgctxt "an4.72:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.72:1.3"
msgid ""
"Nekkhammavitakkena, abyāpādavitakkena, avihiṃsāvitakkena, sammādiṭṭhiyā—"
msgstr "Thoughts of renunciation, love, and kindness; and right view."

msgctxt "an4.72:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu apaṇṇakappaṭipadaṃ "
"paṭipanno hoti, yoni cassa āraddhā hoti āsavānaṃ khayāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant has these four things their practice is guaranteed, and "
"they have laid the groundwork for ending the defilements.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.72:1.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
